## 1. Prerequisites

Before running any scenario:

- [ ] Access to DAPortal via VDI confirmed
- [ ] Requester role assigned in Entra for your account
- [ ] Data Admin role assigned in Entra for approval steps
- [ ] Target sandbox ID confirmed (e.g., `sandbox-001` or equivalent)
- [ ] All test files listed in Section 3 are created and saved locally
- [ ] Azure Storage Explorer access for post-test blob inspection (optional but recommended)
- [ ] Ask the architect the questions in Section 2 before testing - some answers affect expected outcomes

